{"tid":2053744,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"入一入嚟 呢個舊時好多人講嘅廣東話一定要識！仲要煲大佢！","createTime":"2020-06-06T14:15:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T15:04:08.000Z","uid":2104,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9bff5cf4d50d66669a642bdec4fcf94f5dd260ef","tid":2053744,"uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T14:15:40.000Z","msg":"劏豬凳<br />\n<br />\n寫法\t<br />\n繁體： 劏豬凳&mdash;&mdash;<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">上親都死</span></span><br />\n簡體：劏猪凳&mdash;&mdash;上亲都死<br />\n含義\t<br />\n有作「<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">上親就死</span></span>」。劏豬凳係劏豬用嘅工具，通常係將隻豬綁喺劏豬凳上面然後劏殺。「上」除咗可以理解為「將豬綁喺劏豬凳上面」之外，重可以理解為男人同女人發生性行為，因此「劏豬凳」又係用來侮辱嗰啲「剋死丈夫」嘅女性嘅。<br />\n<br />\n【例】<br />\n阿媽：阿仔，同你拍緊拖嗰個女人，之前嫁過兩個老公都死鬼澌。姖唔會係張劏豬凳&mdash;&mdash;上親都死卦？<br />\n阿仔：阿媽啊！你點可以講埋澌啲恁嘅嘢㗎？！你估姖想嘅咩？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>舉例</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uVP5d61.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuVP5d61.jpg&h=3b1b72bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">麻煩大家煲大佢 係劏豬凳<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"9bf3f11c9753a8b4bc3041de55ac1c56eaa55e9b","tid":2053744,"uid":67049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T15:03:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66055f61c512c4e71171c10c1c44b482a48c83d8","tid":2053744,"uid":42982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT